title: SET_DISCORD_RICH_PRESENCE_ACTION
content:
0xCBBC3FAC// SetDiscordRichPresenceAction
void SET_DISCORD_RICH_PRESENCE_ACTION(int index, char* label, char* url);Parameters:index: The button index, either 0 or 1.label: The text to display on the button.url: The URL to open when clicking the button. This has to start with fivem://connect/ or https://.Sets a clickable button to be displayed in a player's Discord rich presence.
